## Spacing Reference

Use `--scale-*` tokens directly for all spacing. No `--space-*` aliases — the scale value is self-documenting.

| Token | Value | Use Case |
|-------|-------|----------|
| `--scale-4` | 4px | Micro gaps |
| `--scale-8` | 8px | Icon padding, tight gaps, inline elements |
| `--scale-12` | 12px | Form field gaps, small component padding |
| `--scale-16` | 16px | Standard padding, card gaps, button padding |
| `--scale-20` | 20px | Medium gaps, card padding (md) |
| `--scale-24` | 24px | Card padding (lg), section gaps |
| `--scale-28` | 28px | Component internal spacing |
| `--scale-32` | 32px | Large component gaps |
| `--scale-36` | 36px | Section padding |
| `--scale-40` | 40px | Large spacing |
| `--scale-48` | 48px | Section margins |
| `--scale-64` | 64px | Page sections |
| `--scale-80` | 80px | Hero spacing |
| `--scale-96` | 96px | Large section breaks |

